{"tid":1845683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「撒回逃犯條例」同「封關」一樣都是林鄭考第一死要面，先搞到一鑊泡","createTime":"2020-01-27T09:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T10:49:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b2b25acd5981bb3212838005641ef83d2cb9ae3b","tid":1845683,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"根本「撒回逃犯條例」, 係要一早要撤, 係事情未變大鑊前要撤, <br />\n林鄭考第一死要面，搞到滿城風雨，最後都係要「撒回」<br />\n仲係令到件事發酵，一發不可收拾<br />\n<br />\n「封關」都係一樣<br />\n奶共林鄭死都要奶, 死都唔封<br />\n係要搞到醫護大罷工<br />\n遟早全港義士流血流汗, 武力封關<br />\n佢先至會死死地氣, 去封<br />\n<br />\n然後, 病毒都已經入到社區大爆發, <br />\n又係一發不可收拾, 滿城風雨<br />\n<br />\n呢條柒婆娘揸旗, 真係仆撚晒街啦！<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉呢D, 只係柒婆身邊既奶共狗官, 科你老母學？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.speakout.hk/articles/cover/20200125/02e57c9dfcfc72f6925bccc44b69cf05.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.speakout.hk%2Farticles%2Fcover%2F20200125%2F02e57c9dfcfc72f6925bccc44b69cf05.jpeg&h=1be08796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/fcwmFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FfcwmFJ.jpg&h=89b73ac5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98f027cfb359069f87ce463c86187b67b769fba5","tid":1845683,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:45:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【科學封關】蒙古國宣布關閉邊境   澳門下令驅逐湖北旅客</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1505061_1_L_20200127130114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1505061_1_L_20200127130114.jpg&h=5998ed3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒙古國宣布，從今天起關閉與中國接壤的邊境通道，包括汽車和行人通道，並呼籲取消所有公眾集會。另外，蒙古今天起，關閉所有大學和教育機構，直至3月2日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505061-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505061-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Ruu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=3d50ed00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505061-20200127.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ed675296\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505061-20200127.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">澳門下令湖北旅客離開澳門 否則強制進入隔離營</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://apple01.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/774-1-696x392.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple01.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F774-1-696x392.png&h=b9716801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是一份昨天流出的澳門旅遊局通告，由澳門旅遊局局長文綺華致全澳各酒店，下令來自武漢市及湖北省的旅客於今早9:00前離開澳門，否則要入住隔離營！先莫論行動效果如何，但至少澳門有實際行動希望減低民怨，但香港呢？就係一招暉明邨？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://apple01.co/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/83238336_2508125362767377_512583322912686080_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple01.co%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F83238336_2508125362767377_512583322912686080_n.jpg&h=380760e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e48c88c8fd84b3a1dd2b502b76c523084f53bd1f","tid":1845683,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:48:15.000Z","msg":"佢想我地團結姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靜靜地贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#WeConnect"},{"pid":"705e8133b6d03e33515b0b04c175ba27c131db55","tid":1845683,"uid":262557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"跟本依家就要推翻政府"},{"pid":"a404c24a4d3f2f9641e44e1f7f47ed80931db29c","tid":1845683,"uid":184628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b2e91ecbc18a7b46d5f7c3e27f9391efb5573e61","tid":1845683,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27